sql:
SELECT SUM(shares_owned) 
FROM portfolio 
WHERE user_id = 0;

SELECT company_code, shares_owned, purchase_price
FROM portfolio
WHERE user_id = 1;

SELECT company_code, AVG(confidence_level) as "Average Confidence Level"
FROM market_analytics
GROUP BY company_code;

external_knowledge:
Significant number of shares refers to more than 100 shares;
Investors are referred to as users in the system;
Contact emails are used for communication purposes.

sql:
SELECT c.company_name, sp.price_per_share
FROM companies c
JOIN stock_prices sp ON c.company_code = sp.company_code;

SELECT DISTINCT u.user_name
FROM users u
JOIN expert_blogs eb ON u.user_id = eb.user_id;

external_knowledge:
- 'digital ecosystem': the technology sector;
- 'shimmering tech giants': companies in the Technology sector;
- 'reflective stock prices': price per share of the companies;
- 'economic mirage': stock exchanges located in the USA.

